text:
Yo Abhijeet. Orientation week se start hui apni journey and phir to saath hi rahe humesha. Saath me PE, saath me classes. Yaad hai first year me tujhe bahut terms ka matab nhi pta hota tha phir mai batata tha tujhe, khair ab to sab seekh gya hai tu. First year me mast AI seekha tune lol. Puppy love me wo mails bhejne ke baad lag rha tha ki chaap hi dia humne, but kuch reaction nhi mila. First aur second year me maximum time to mai tumlogo ke room pe hi rha hu. Tune na jane kitni hi apni school ki aur delhi ki stories sunai hai. Mast stories thi waise. Saath mil ke bhole ki aakhein bhi to kholi hain humne. Wo 400m race aur medal bhi yaad rahega. Mso202 me mast phati thi apni phir sab wing me zameen pe baithe the depressed, phir 203 to kya aaram se nikala tha. 3rd year me apni shop C trips, kafi nutirion pe focus. (Lol weight phir bhi nhi badha mera). Kafi maza aaya hai tere saath. Sadly apni trip nhi hui koi. Bbq me kya pel khaya hai humne. Mai, tu aur tarish bbq and 3 movies lagataar. Inte pass rehte hain apan par ye covid aur bihar ke tatti infra ke karan mil nhi pa rhe. Milte hain jaldi hi.
P.S.: Ab to eye test karwa le.
author: Abhinav  Ankit

text:
Yo Moond. Apni to itni memories hai kya kya hi likhu. Apne room se zayda to shyad mai tere room pe hi raha hounga first year se hi. First year me apan exam dene se phle my **** sun ke jaate the enthu badhane ke lie. Lol yaad hai 1st year summer me apan gye the e-club ka test dene aur hume nhi lia tha aur R****** ko le lia tha. Humne maximum course saath me hi kie hain aur tu mujhe cycle pe bitha ke le jata tha. 2nd year udghosh me mere meme banane ke baad loda ne chutiyapa kia tha fir tune id banai thi. Bahut bakchod thi wo id waise. Bhola tujhe vc na karta to aur use hota us id ka. 
Best time apna to 2nd year summer hi raha hai. Pure din bas bulla session chalte rehte the. Ek baar mai tu jai mil ke tujhe shaadi se bhagane ki planning kar rhe the jiska kharcha teri bmw bech ke aata. 3rd year ka winter bhi apna bahut interesting hi raha tha. Pehle quiz ko leke batti gang me dispute hua. Phir tune chapa dia tha jisko sun ke mai full shocked tha. Phir prank ke chakkar me batti gang me phir dispute hua tha. Jisko sort karne ke lie maine bahut lamba msg likha tha jo tu maan nhi rha tha ki maine likha hai. ( Ab to maan lena, wo maine khud se hi likha tha) In sab ko mast new year party ke saath conclude kia tha. 
Uske baad to lockdown me hi beet gya pichla saal. Abhi mai last me aaya hota to maza aata but koi nhi apan to milte hi rahenge. 
PS: Humesha aise hi logic lagate rehna.
author: Abhinav  Ankit

author: Abhinav  Ankit

text: Yo bro. Apan to kota se zaante hain ek dusre ko par tab zayda baat nhi hui thi. Yahan to pta nhi kitne assignments aur exams saath nikale hain humne. Thora pubg bhi khele saath me. Maza aaya hai tere saath interact karne me. Chalo all the best for your future hopefully jaldi milenge.
author: Abhinav  Ankit

text:
Here we go. Apne first sem ke zayda moments to yaad nhi hain mujhe. But ek incident yaad hai, tu mere room pe aaya tha TA101 ke assignment se related kuch puchne. Phir maine pucha tha ki class jata hai, to tune bola nhi. Phir maine bola tha akhand chutiyapa. To tune bola tha ‚Äúoye dhang se‚Äù. We‚Äôve come a long way from there. 
Saare courses to saath kie hain humne. Jab apne departmental courses start hue the to tu Dhr** Pu***** ke saath class me baithta tha, phir maine aur moond ne maze lie the tere.
4th sem me humne apni paathshala banai. (Moond: Atif ko add kar. Jai: Abe nhi apni harkatein bhi to hongi na) Messages that aged well. Kaise na kaise karke nikal hi lie saare courses. 210 to khair zindagi bhar yaad rahega. Kya phati thi apni. Khair courses to bahut chota part hai apni memories ka. 
Second-year summer to best tha. Subah class se aate phir pure din chill karte. Bahut gyaan prapt kia aur baata tha. Moond ko shadi se bhagane ki planning karna. 3rd year ka winter to kya hi special hai apne lie. Start me quiz ko leke choda hua phir mere aur moond ke prank ke chakkar me tu naraz ho gya tha. Fir maine 2 bade paragraphs likhe the cheezo ko clear karne ke lie. Jo moond maan nhi rha tha ki maine likhe. Anyways we sorted that and ended up being more closer. Phir new year party se mast conclude kia tha cheezo ko. Phir uske baad to ye corono hi aa gya. Kuch bhi ho you‚Äôve always been there for me whenever I needed you. And this is what makes our bond specialüíö
Ab hindsight me cheezein dekhta hu to bahut achcha lagta hai. As a person jo khud ka improvement dekhta hu usme tum logo ka hi major influence hai. 
Wo sex education ka clip yaad hai jisme wo payara wisdom hai aur lauv ka i like me better ye to kitne pasand hain apne ko. Bas apni koi trip nhi hui saath me. Khair abhi to bahut trips karni hain. Bachelor party bhi to karni hai foreign me. Hopefully jaldi milte hain bahut bakchodi karni baaki hai abhi.
author: Abhinav  Ankit

text: Yo Katiyar. Kafi mast banda hai tu maza aaya hai tere saath interaction me. Aise hi hardworking bane raho aur chaapte raho. All the best.
author: Abhinav  Ankit

text:
Yo Bhole. E6 me wingi se start kie phir dheere dheere itna close bond develop ho gya. Kitna pubg khele hain hum log. Specially AOB squad. Yaad hai thermo wale ne hum teeno ko class se bhaga dia tha. Lol tab bhi pubg hi discuss kar rhe the class me. 
Us sem mai bolta tha tujhe ki tera A nhi lagega, phir maine khud ne hag dia tha xD.
Jab tune story sunai thi tab mai aur Abhijeet full surprised the. Abhijeet to bahut zayda hi shocked tha. Tab realise hua ki tu bas naam se hi bhola hai.(Wiase aakhein khol di thi humne teri.) Second year me to apna room bagal me tha. Mai to pada rehta tha tumhare room pe. Bahut maze kie hain. 2 trips ka plan banaya tha tere saath but dono me kat gya mai. Koi nhi karenge jab milte hain. 
PS: Paise sambhal ke rakhna apne, bahar bahot log hain lootne wale.
author: Abhinav  Ankit

text: Yo Dechi. Apan zayda mile nhi but kafi maza aaya hai tere saath pubg khel ke. Phir khelenge abhi thora launch hone de.

text:
Yo roomie. Apan to ek dusre ko kota se jaante hain. Tab to kafi kam baat hui thi. Jis din campus aaya tha to list dekha ki roommate kon hai. Phir dekha ki is bande ko to pehle se janta hu mai. Jab start me seniors raat ko darwaza thoke the aur apna kholte nhi the dar se. Pta nhi kyu bc mai, tu aur bhole udghosh me gye. First  year summer me mast pubg khelte the apan aur tu kya bakchod peek karta tha aur wo TA me top view dekhna lol. Mai, tu, das aur bhole pta nhi match saath khele the. Lol AOB squad. 
Kai baar jab mai beemar padta tha to tu mujhe cycle pe bitha ke HC le jata tha. Tujhe itna padhta dekh ke mai bhi padh lia thora. Mai apne room se zayda to dusro ke room me bhatakta rehta tha.
Apni ek bhi trip nhi ho paai kyuki mai kat jata tha. Ab jab milenge tab karte hain ek trip.

Yo Tarish. Pta nhi tu ye khol ke dekhega bhi ya nhi. Har cheez ka gyan hota hai tera pass. Pubg aur apex me bahut interest tha tujhe but khelne me bahut bada noob hai. Tere saath treats me bahut maza aaya hai. Kai baar to disputes bhi hue veg aur non-veg walo me xD. Himachal aur Sikkim trip ka plan banaya tere saath but gya nhi. Hopefully karenge ek trip to. Kabhi mauka milega to cook karenge apan saath me. 
PS: Will miss going to bbq with you.
